episodes.title: End Times Cult - Iris
episodes.description:
In this emotional and eye-opening episode of Human: Unfiltered, Iris shares their journey of resilience and survival after escaping an end-of-days cult. Growing up in an environment filled with control, fear, and abuse, Iris endured unimaginable trauma that left lasting scars. They open up about the guilt they carried, the pain that led to self-harm, and the challenges of rebuilding their life after breaking free.

Iris's story is a raw and powerful reminder of the human spirit's ability to persevere, even in the face of profound adversity.

💬 Join the conversation in the comments, and if this story resonates with you, please consider subscribing for more unfiltered stories.

If you or someone you know is struggling with self-harm or the effects of abuse, resources are available to help. You are not alone.

If you have a story to tell, email us at humanunfilteredstories@gmail.com
